Runing Vitualbox Remotely

http://www.virtualbox.org/manual/ch08.html

sudo -H -u server2 VBoxManage startvm "Centos_bacula" --type headless


The extra --type option causes VirtualBox to use VBoxHeadless as the front-end to the internal virtualization engine instead of the Qt front-end. 

http://www.virtualbox.org/manual/ch07.html#vboxheadless

I add also sudo usermod -a -G vboxusers server2
